{"tid":1628758,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(改變壞習慣）唔駛叫阿SIR，叫警察/差人/差佬即可。","createTime":"2019-10-06T04:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T10:12:23.000Z","uid":104965,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"faacaa124db2cca42efe5bd12fd8610f54a46662","tid":1628758,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:34:45.000Z","msg":"「阿Sir」係稱呼一啲對社會有貢獻或者高級過自己嘅人員，例如醫院入邊的病房助理都會叫男護士阿sir。<br />\n<br />\n作為一個不滿意現時香港警務人員的普通市民，請不要再稱呼香港警務人員為阿sir<br />\n<br />\n有禮貌的我只會稱警察先生/女士<br />\n無禮貌的我只會稱做差人/差婆<br />\n當然當面叫警犬/黑警也無可厚非<br />\n<br />\n請記住！<br />\n呢一個改變係要警務人員認清自己已經不再受香港市民的敬重，奪去他們引以為傲的優越感，讓他們再認清楚他們現時在社會的地位越來越差，唔好再比大媽讚兩句就含晒春咁撚樣。"},{"pid":"403a1c68000221791a29eae9078613c42b3e6c1e","tid":1628758,"uid":64469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:41:37.000Z","msg":"唔好意思想重推！麻煩入一入黎睇下你既角色定位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［我有野講］咪撚再唱歌叫口號［入黎睇下自己衰咩］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1612280\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1612280</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3c8fa451853deaddf362b5bc9d140a21ddf68c05","tid":1628758,"uid":108016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:43:02.000Z","msg":"叫 pc 啦"},{"pid":"2c1f14a5babf14187b151e0d92ecd65ce00191db","tid":1628758,"uid":24842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:43:30.000Z","msg":"叫開狗"},{"pid":"78963b757ec8287073b09d927ecc2a217bb9a2a0","tid":1628758,"uid":275688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:44:07.000Z","msg":"狗"},{"pid":"0141c1c30962553f64f15792a99c78d2f3049692","tid":1628758,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c8fa451853deaddf362b5bc9d140a21ddf68c05","tid":1628758,"uid":108016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:43:02.000Z","msg":"叫 pc 啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:52:30.000Z","msg":"已經好有禮貌了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif